New paint, granite countertops, kitchen cabinets, new luxury vinyl plank flooring, new baseboards and crown molding, new bathroom vanities and much more. What the seller loves about the home is the location, of being central to Kernersville, Greensboro, High Point and Winston Salem. The seller loves the spacious rooms and the yard. Heatpump replaced in 2015.
